Hi,

These “AV” parts cannot be sold as stand alone parts.  They are used in a custom build. 

You would need to provide a BD from HP to purchase along with a certified BOM.

 

Thank You,

Joe Gibson

Vendor Business Manager

HP Personal Systems Group
